column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID,round(p.ra,#) as ra,round(p.dec,#) as dec,round(p.u,#) as PhotoOb_u,round(p.g,#) as PhotoOb_g,round(p.r,#) as PhotoOb_r, round(p.i,#) as PhotoOb_i,round(p.err_u,#) as err_u, round(p.err_g,#) as err_g, round(p.err_r,#) as err_r, round(P.err_i,#) as err_i, round(p.petroR5#_r,#) as petroR5#_r, round(p.petroR5#Err_r,#) as petroR5#Err_r,round(p.z,#) as PhotoObj_z, p.type, /*specObj table parameters*/ s.specobjid, s.class, s.subClass, round(s.z,#) as spec_redshift, round(s.zErr,#) as spec_redshift_Err,round(s.zWarning,#) as Spec_redshift_Warning FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
